<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: April 27, 2026</p>

  <p class="text-gray-700">Your name and email will be used solely by Clean Up the City to send our once-weekly volunteer newsletter, track aggregate participation statistics such as cleanup attendance, and audit restaurant invoices. Your information will not be used for any other purpose and will never be shared with any other organization.</p>
